author: The Critical Drinker
description:
We're feeling particularly empowered on Open Bar this week as Red Sonja inspired us all to do better. Not to worry though, we've still got the growing disaster of Avengers Doomsday to laugh at, and Last of Us Season 3 which is apparently filming without even having finished scripts. Join me, MauLer, Disparu, Echo Chamberlain and KingKreese as we talk about it. 

Subscribe to Disparu: https://www.youtube.com/@disparutoo
Subscribe to Echo: https://www.youtube.com/@EchoChamberlain
Subscribe to KingKreese: https://www.youtube.com/@forthehomiespodcast288
title: Open Bar #155 - Red Sonja, Avengers Doomsday Chaos, Last Of Us Season 3
